{
  "texts": [
    "That may be explained by the fact that our data included an older cohort.",
    "Hobson et al.",
    "have observed that marriage is getting more stressful for older adults [6].In line with other studies, we have found that incarceration is a significant barrier to CRC screening [41].",
    "In our study, we were able to show that not only currently detained but also patients with a history of incarceration had, indeed, much lower screening rates.",
    "This prompts for targeted interventions for this vulnerable population.Losing access to financial resources due to unexpected job loss or becoming homeless expectedly reduced the chances of screening."
  ]
}